snippet: Brandt Jobe, in only his third tournament round in seven months since sustaining herniated cervical disks, was near the top of the leader board at the Northern Trust Open.
abstract: Brandt Jobe, in only his third tournament round in seven months since sustaining herniated cervical disks, is near top of leader board after first round at Northern Trust Open golf tournament.
lead_paragraph: Brandt Jobe, in only his third tournament round in seven months since sustaining herniated cervical disks, was near the top of the leader board at the Northern Trust Open.
